<br>
But, there will be a few that are not purchasable. Think about BO IV, Muzzle, and a few others that you either see only occasionally there or not at all.<br>
<br>
Wouldnt it be a good idea for VI to check those numbers and adjust drop rates/locations of those rare spells spells? I mean you can get dozens of copies of Bristlebanes Bundle, but I havent seen BO IV since Bazaar openend.<br>
<br>
